<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1869-08-13T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1869-08-13T00:00:00-05:00" n="299" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d299">
                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Davis</persName>, Acting
                                    Secretary of State, to Mr. <persName type="to">Hoar</persName>,
                                    Attorney General.</hi>
                            </head>
                            <dateline><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Department of
                                        State</hi>,<lb/><hi rend="italic">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1869-08-13"><hi rend="italic">August</hi> 13,
                                1869</date>.</dateline>
                            <p><hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I give you herewith, for your
                                information, a transcript of a letter from the Acting Secretary of
                                the Navy, of the 11th instant, relative te the transfer of the
                                Spanish gun-boats which were recently <pb facs="0754" n="740" xml:id="pg_740"/> seized by order of the President, to the
                                custody *of the commandant of the navy-yard at New York. <seg type="margin">[768]</seg></p>
                            <p>I am, sir, &amp;c.,</p>
                            <closer>
                                <signed>J. C. B. DAVIS,<lb/><hi rend="italic">Acting
                                    Secretary.</hi></signed>
                            </closer>
                            <postscript>
                                <p>The Hon. <hi rend="smallcaps">E. R. Hoar</hi>,<lb/><hi rend="italic">Attorney-General.</hi></p>
                                <p>[For inclosure see <hi rend="italic">ante</hi>, p. 739.]</p>
                            </postscript>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>